      "id": "s1_sort_note",
      "x": 96,
      "y": 552,
      "width": 488,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "Batches sort by (layer, batchIdx); within a batch, instances\nsort by zIndex — batchSortSystem, in-place swapSlots.\n\nMany sprites sharing one material collapse into one draw call.",
