      "x": 758,
      "y": 910,
      "width": 524,
      "height": 62,
      "text": "addEffect(Dissolve)    → flags |=  (1 << bitIdx)\nremoveEffect(Dissolve) → flags &= ~(1 << bitIdx)\n→ mesh.writeEnableBits(slot, flags)   // 1 float write",
